{"tid":1189394,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"人越大 越覺得自己越睇錢","createTime":"2019-06-06T18:42:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-06T18:51:01.000Z","uid":205742,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"07f0e64f7c580b6e582cf2147015c0c748a680d2","tid":1189394,"uid":205742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T18:42:48.000Z","msg":"用少少錢都諗過度過，識對象都會睇下對方嘅背景，唔係再好似以前咁有愛就乜都得，以前細個真係太幸福，可以喺無憂無慮嘅環境下生活，從來唔使擔心錢嘅問題，到出咗嚟社會個人就變到好自私，一毛不拔、錙銖必較<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n究竟係我太貪錢，定其實個個都會係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"616df80c0a0878490e3c1f3350a0af6f4a794a71","tid":1189394,"uid":242224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T18:44:44.000Z","msg":"on9, 你姐"},{"pid":"6f6ea83f264aa211fe002f7deed33c1ff6b120cb","tid":1189394,"uid":205742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"616df80c0a0878490e3c1f3350a0af6f4a794a71","tid":1189394,"uid":242224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T18:44:44.000Z","msg":"on9, 你姐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T18:45:44.000Z","msg":"ok"},{"pid":"4e68fa35cc5aee4c09cec9a9bf2ae975ef9d6a39","tid":1189394,"uid":191815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T18:51:01.000Z","msg":"你唔係貪錢<br />\n你窮啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}